02:21.226 --> 02:23.294
Wait, you mean I told you this already?

02:23.295 --> 02:24.528
Yes.

02:24.529 --> 02:26.035
For real?

02:29.234 --> 02:31.769
This news is even sadder
the second time around.

02:35.240 --> 02:36.907
Grandma, how have you been feeling?

02:36.908 --> 02:38.976
Well, it's been a struggle,

02:38.977 --> 02:40.978
but I'm feeling better
now that I've decided

02:40.979 --> 02:43.247
to take matters into my own hands

02:43.248 --> 02:46.283
and end my life myself.

02:47.853 --> 02:49.386
- Mom.
- Oh, I'm sorry,

02:49.387 --> 02:51.522
have I... did I tell you
that news already, too?

02:53.525 --> 02:57.428
No, you didn't tell us that news.

02:57.429 --> 02:59.763
Good, then that's the news
I wanted to tell you.

03:01.566 --> 03:03.801
♪

03:10.268 --> 03:16.868
<font color="#FFDF00">Subtitle sync and corrections by</font>
